{"tid":2234820,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中槍健仔擬認暴動罪 寄語香港人：「唔好放棄，堅持到底」","createTime":"2020-10-08T07:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T15:25:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":22,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"f530804316aa97da7c57ee1ce7e732a7e8bf9c5b","tid":2234820,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T07:29:20.000Z","msg":"18歲中五男生「健仔」曾志健去年10月1日在荃灣遭警員實彈槍傷，事後被控一項暴動罪及兩項襲警罪；當日跑到中槍「健仔」身旁大叫「救人先」的理工大學博士生亦被控暴動。兩人的案件今在區域法院提訊，控方申請將案押後，指需與辯方商討案情，「想達成共識同案情調整，言下之意，第一被告（「健仔」）之後應該會認罪」，案件押後至12月22日再訊，兩人准以同樣條件保釋候訊。<br />\n<br />\n聆訊前，「健仔」稱有心理準備或需還柙，他步入犯人欄前寄語香港人：「唔好放棄，堅持到底」。被問到認罪的決定是否基於家人或學業的考慮，健仔透露與律師商量後，認為「認罪係最好嘅決定」；他坦言有心理準備將會坐監，但相信在此前仍有一連串的法律程序需要處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201008/JO7Q7GONXJHKXGVIQKZZHTPQRA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2FJO7Q7GONXJHKXGVIQKZZHTPQRA%2F&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5OxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=b680bc38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2FJO7Q7GONXJHKXGVIQKZZHTPQRA%2F&h=38beef23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201008/JO7Q7GONXJHKXGVIQKZZHTPQRA/</a>"},{"pid":"4bbde231d73e3fe95123f43cada8c69a3f872589","tid":2234820,"uid":76804,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T07:29:51.000Z","msg":"點解要認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e410b8b819052def707f3ab45541f5ef052acc","tid":2234820,"uid":141668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T07:30:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89b3cc5ef6f33a2ccadd6d8ecd8304684c04950","tid":2234820,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T07:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d7307d08c4d84082e16a785a44aadaa2fa020c","tid":2234820,"uid":